Context: The George Brown College IELTS Test Centre will be closed from December 23, 2023 to January 2, 2024. It can be contacted at ielts@georgebrown.ca during this period. The test centre will reopen on January 3, 2024. Those looking to book an IELTS test are encouraged to email ielts@georgebrown.ca for information on adding test dates and seating. The IELTS Canada website provides more information about IELTS in Canada. IELTS is jointly owned by British Council, IDP: IELTS Australia, and Cambridge English Language Assessment. The contact numbers for George Brown College are 416-415-2000 and TTY: 1-877-515-5559. Emails can also be sent to ask.george@georgebrown.ca. For updates on application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and more, sign up now.
